i>; &lt;li id=&quot; KA11HN&quot;>;超超和超超宽显示器支持&lt;/li>; &lt;li id=&quot;ylQQAs&quot;>;鼠标和键盘支持（自然）&lt;/li>; &lt;li id=&quot;wEZOHa&quot;>;升级技术支持 Nvidia DLSS 3.7 和AMD FSR 3.0&lt;/li>; &lt;li id=&quot;216Hwd&quot;>;Nvidia DLSS 帧生成&lt;/li>; &lt;li id=&quot;pIF5YB&quot;>;可调节绘制距离和阴影质量设置&lt;/li>; &lt;/ul>; &lt;p id= &quot;9hniik&quot;>;去年，Rockstar 在 PS4 和 Nintendo Switch 上发布了《RDR》移植版。根据&lt;em>;Verge&lt;/em>;作家安德鲁·韦伯斯特的说法，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/8/17/23834520/red-dead-redemption-nintendo-switch-hands-on &quot;>;&lt;em>;Red Dead Redemption 有效...&lt;/a>;&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/8/24265128/ red-dead-redemption-undead-nightmare-pc-october-29th&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/8/24265128/red-dead-redemption-undead-nightmare-pc-october-29th" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/8/24265128/red-dead-redemption-undead-nightmare-pc-october-29th</id><author><name>阿什·帕里什</name></author></entry></feed>